@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Employee Device" as User
rectangle "ZTNA / VPN Gateway" as Access
rectangle "Enterprise App Zone\nIntranet Apps" as EntApps
rectangle "Shared Services\nIAM, DNS, Logging" as Shared
rectangle "Forward Proxy" as FP
rectangle "Egress Firewall" as EF
cloud "Internet / SaaS" as Internet

User --> Access : Authenticated session
Access --> EntApps : App access
EntApps --> Shared : Internal dependencies
EntApps --> FP : Outbound request
FP --> EF : URL/category policy
EF --> Internet : Allowlisted egress
Internet --> EF
EF --> FP
FP --> EntApps

note bottom of FP
Outbound paths are logged,
filtered, and policy-enforced.
end note
@enduml

